column5: Coming soon to a lake near you!
22" of ice on Nipissing today says the fishing season will be closed long before the ice ever melts
By the end of next week we'll have even more snow than last winter I bet...yeehaw!  Against all odds, it turned out to be a great year to buy a new sled
Yeah in NW ontario we have 5" of snow and plus temps, go figure...  Enjoy it guys!
Was on a solid clear 10" today. The problem is, when the warmer temps come, the shore line is the question. If I get another two weeks, Im good.
